reviewText: This movie is OK , my kids are really into the angry birds stuff , but I noticed that a lot of the episode's are the same as in volume one !!  But for the price it keeps my kids happy for almost an hour.

This volume of Season Two is great. I am a huge Angry Birds fan.
The special features in this DVD are great. I am so happy that I have added that to my 'Angry Birds Toons' DVD collection.
